    "zh": "提出了一个控制框架，用于在没有全球目标的未映射环境中配备Ackermann转向的移动机器人的安全本地导航"
  },
  "A new class of agentic review systems are emerging as a remedy to the pressure placed on peer review systems by AI-assisted research, but it is unclear how they should be evaluated": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:30.765279+00:00",
    "zh": "一种新的代理评审系统正在出现，作为对人工智能辅助研究对同行评审系统施加压力的补救措施，但目前尚不清楚应如何对其进行评估"
  },
  "Academic paper search is a core step in scientific research, and LLM-based search agents are emerging as a promising paradigm for iterative, intent-driven literature exploration": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:08.334329+00:00",
    "zh": "学术论文搜索是科学研究的核心步骤，基于法学硕士的搜索代理正在成为迭代、意图驱动的文献探索的一个有前途的范例"
  },
  "Air-ground collaborative perception is crucial for robust visual understanding in real-world dynamic environments": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:20.924102+00:00",
    "zh": "地空协作感知对于真实动态环境中的强大视觉理解至关重要"
  },
  "Art has long stood as a pivotal expression of human creativity": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:17.967045+00:00",
    "zh": "艺术长期以来一直是人类创造力的关键表现形式"
  },
  "As LLM agents increasingly select tools autonomously, their choices among tools with different privileges become safety-relevant": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:12.864340+00:00",
    "zh": "随着LLM代理越来越多地自主选择工具，他们在具有不同权限的工具之间的选择变得与安全相关"
  },
  "As large language models (LLMs) advance and multi-agent systems aim to overcome the limits of standalone agents, robust communication protocols are becoming essential infrastructure for distributed agent networks": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:10.281951+00:00",
    "zh": "随着大语言模型（ LLM ）的进步和多智能体系统旨在克服独立智能体的局限性，强大的通信协议正成为分布式智能体网络的必不可少的基础设施"
  },
  "Automated vulnerability discovery in large codebases remains challenging: traditional static analysis produces high false-positive rates, while dynamic approaches such as fuzzing require substantial infrastructure and often target narrow classes of bugs": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:13.734462+00:00",
    "zh": "大型代码库中的自动化漏洞发现仍然具有挑战性：传统的静态分析产生高误报率，而模糊处理等动态方法需要大量基础设施，并且通常针对狭窄的漏洞类别"
  },
  "Autonomous agentic AI systems driven by Large Language Models (LLMs) introduce a new class of security, privacy, and compliance challenges: an agent that can invoke tools, manipulate data, install software, and coordinate with peer agents across organizational": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:25.370519+00:00",
    "zh": "由大语言模型(LLM)驱动的自主代理人工智能系统引入了一类新的安全、隐私和合规性挑战：一个可以调用工具、操纵数据、安装软件并与组织中的同行代理进行协调的代理"
  },
  "Autonomous agents are increasingly connected to cloud, deployment, and data-control workflows, but production mutation authority should not reside inside non-deterministic reasoning processes": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:03.802287+00:00",
    "zh": "自治代理越来越多地连接到云、部署和数据控制工作流程，但生产突变权限不应驻留在非确定性推理过程中"
  },
  "Bayesian predictive inference provides a principled framework for uncertainty quantification, data efficiency, and robust generalization": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:28.076373+00:00",
    "zh": "贝叶斯预测推断为不确定性量化、数据效率和鲁棒泛化提供了一个原则框架"
  },
  "Benchmark infrastructure for personally identifiable information (PII) detection remains limited: existing corpora cover few entity types, use ad hoc generation conditions, and do not show which surface conditions cause detector failures": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:42.845205+00:00",
    "zh": "用于个人身份信息（ PII ）检测的基准基础设施仍然有限：现有语料库涵盖的实体类型很少，使用临时生成条件，并且不显示导致检测器故障的表面条件"
  },
  "Block diffusion language models accelerate decoding through parallel block-wise denoising, yet whether they can be reliably scaled for long chain-of-thought (CoT) reasoning remains unresolved": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:27.671080+00:00",
    "zh": "块扩散语言模型通过并行块去噪加速解码，但它们是否可以可靠地缩放以用于长思维链（ CoT ）推理仍未解决"
  },
  "Byte-Pair Encoding tokenization is statistically efficient for vocabulary compression, but semantically blind to structured technical entities, fragmenting physical quantities, numbers, units, and symbolic expressions into lexically arbitrary subwords": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:06.873206+00:00",
    "zh": "字节对编码标记化在词汇压缩方面具有统计效率，但在语义上对结构化技术实体视而不见，将物理量、数字、单位和符号表达式分割成词汇任意子词"
  },
  "Camera-trap monitoring in African tropical forests increasingly extends beyond closed-canopy interiors to riverbanks, clearings, and park edges": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:09.085493+00:00",
    "zh": "非洲热带森林的摄像机陷阱监测越来越多地从封闭的树冠内部延伸到河岸、空地和公园边缘"
  },
  "Charged-particle tracking -- reconstructing trajectories from sparse detector measurements -- is a fundamental high-energy-physics inference problem and a canonical example of learning under extreme combinatorial ambiguity": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:34.964184+00:00",
    "zh": "带电粒子跟踪--从稀疏探测器测量重建轨迹--是一个基本的高能物理推理问题，也是极端组合歧义下学习的一个典型例子"
  },
  "Conditional diffusion and flow models routinely fail to satisfy the very constraints that define their task": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:02.280005+00:00",
    "zh": "条件扩散和流程模型通常无法满足定义其任务的约束条件"
  },
  "Continual Test-Time Adaptation (CTTA) aims to maintain model performance under evolving target domains by adapting online without labeled data": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:37.606533+00:00",
    "zh": "持续测试时间自适应（ CTTA ）旨在通过在线调整无标记数据来保持模型在不断变化的目标域下的性能"
  },
  "Current machine learning models commonly require large and well-annotated datasets": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:16.497353+00:00",
    "zh": "当前的机器学习模型通常需要大型且注释良好的数据集"
  },
  "Decentralized finance exposes supervisors to fast-moving, networked credit risks": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:17.045572+00:00",
    "zh": "去中心化金融使主管面临快速移动、网络化的信用风险"
  },
  "Deep research agents have demonstrated remarkable capabilities in autonomous information gathering and synthesis, yet their training remains constrained by the static nature of simulated environments, the limits of fact-retrieval-only task designs, and the ine": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:41.954025+00:00",
    "zh": "深度研究机构在自主信息收集和合成方面表现出非凡的能力，但他们的训练仍然受到模拟环境的静态性质，仅事实检索任务设计的局限性以及"
  },
  "Deepfakes targeting a high-profile individual, known as Person-of-Interest (POI), are a threat to modern democracies and societies": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:49.502714+00:00",
    "zh": "针对高调个人（称为利益相关者（ POI ） ）的深度伪造对现代民主和社会构成威胁"
  },
  "Existing graph-based multi-agent system (MAS) designers mainly improve collaboration by optimizing communication topologies over predefined agents, roles, or groups": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:43.696755+00:00",
    "zh": "现有的基于图形的多代理系统(MAS)设计人员主要通过优化预定义的代理、角色或组的通信拓扑来改善协作"
  },
  "Existing multi-speaker dialogue systems bind speakers to utterances through structured supervision: per-turn tags, multi-stream transcriptions, or learnable speaker embeddings": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:26.100720+00:00",
    "zh": "现有的多发言者对话系统通过结构化监督将发言者与话语绑定：每轮标签、多流转录或可学习的发言者嵌入"
  },
  "Existing safety benchmarks target general adversarial scenarios but miss finance-specific risks": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:20:59.988950+00:00",
    "zh": "现有的安全基准针对一般对抗情景，但忽略了财务特定风险"
  },
  "Flow matching has emerged as a standard paradigm for robotic manipulation owing to its strong expressive power for modelling complex, multimodal action distributions, alongside similar approaches like diffusion policy": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:28.984601+00:00",
    "zh": "流量匹配已经成为机器人操作的标准范例，因为它具有很强的表达能力，可以对复杂的多模态动作分布进行建模，同时还具有扩散策略等类似方法"
  },
  "For embodied agents capable of physical interaction, the capability to create and understand dialog is crucial to ensure both safety and effectiveness": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:14.330239+00:00",
    "zh": "对于能够进行身体互动的具体客服代表，创建和理解对话的能力对于确保安全和有效性至关重要"
  },
  "Glioma segmentation in multiparametric MRI is a critical component of treatment planning": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:26.898472+00:00",
    "zh": "多参数MRI中的胶质瘤分割是治疗计划的重要组成部分"
  },
  "Grapheme-to-phoneme (G2P) conversion for Modern Hebrew is needed for applications like text-to-speech (TTS), but is challenging due to the language's abjad writing system, which leaves vowels largely unwritten, creating substantial ambiguity": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:09.908225+00:00",
    "zh": "现代希伯来语的语素到音素（ G2P ）转换是文本到语音（ TTS ）等应用程序所必需的，但由于该语言的abjad书写系统使元音基本上不成文，因此具有挑战性，从而产生了很大的歧义"
  },
  "Human visual attention relies on structured scanpaths to efficiently process scenes, yet instilling this behavior into robot autonomy is in its infancy and hindered by the high,computational costs of existing predictive models": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:46.191849+00:00",
    "zh": "人类的视觉注意力依赖于结构化扫描路径来有效地处理场景，但是将这种行为灌输到机器人自主性中还处于起步阶段，并受到现有预测模型高昂的计算成本的阻碍"
  },
  "Humanoid robots require co-speech motions that are not only expressive and speech-aligned, but also physically executable under embodiment constraints": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:15.824034+00:00",
    "zh": "人形机器人需要的共语运动不仅具有表达能力和语音一致性，而且在实施例约束下具有物理可执行性"
  },
  "In multimodal video reasoning, reinforcement learning-based methods typically rely on simplistic and inflexible reasoning-length control strategies that fail to adapt to the model's evolving competence": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:17.314843+00:00",
    "zh": "在多模态视频推理中，基于强化学习的方法通常依赖于简单和不灵活的推理长度控制策略，这些策略无法适应模型不断发展的能力"
  },
  "LLM-based coding agents need higher-level operational knowledge about a repository (which files house which subsystems, how to run the test suite, which workflows have historically led to wrong fixes) that does not exist in the code itself": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:31.714831+00:00",
    "zh": "基于LLM的编码代理需要更高级别的操作知识，了解代码本身不存在的存储库（存储哪些子系统、如何运行测试套件、哪些工作流程历来导致错误的修复）"
  },
  "Large Language Model (LLM)-based automatic Multi-Agent Systems (MAS) generation has become a crucial frontier for tackling complex tasks": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:21.687366+00:00",
    "zh": "基于大语言模型（ LLM ）的自动多Agent系统（ MAS ）生成已成为处理复杂任务的关键前沿"
  },
  "Large Language Models (LLMs) have shown strong capabilities in general-purpose code generation, but their effectiveness in specialized software domains remains underexplored": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:13.611490+00:00",
    "zh": "大语言模型（ LLM ）在通用代码生成方面表现出强大的能力，但其在专业软件领域的有效性仍未得到充分探索"
  },
  "Large language model (LLM) agents are increasingly proposed as supervisory components for safety-critical systems, yet their robustness under sustained, adaptive adversarial pressure remains poorly characterized": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:05.283204+00:00",
    "zh": "大语言模型（ LLM ）代理越来越多地被提出作为安全关键系统的监督组件，但它们在持续、自适应对抗压力下的鲁棒性仍然很差"
  },
  "Large language models (LLMs) are increasingly deployed in sensitive settings such as software engineering, where their outputs directly shape downstream artifacts": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:12.800859+00:00",
    "zh": "大语言模型（ LLM ）越来越多地部署在软件工程等敏感环境中，其输出直接影响下游工件"
  },
  "Large language models (LLMs) can make clinical decision support more accessible by interpreting free-text documentation, but their direct use as diagnostic engines is limited by sensitivity to prompts, information order, and plausible but incorrect outputs": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:11.977158+00:00",
    "zh": "大语言模型（ LLM ）可以通过解释自由文本文档使临床决策支持更容易获得，但它们作为诊断引擎的直接用途受到对提示、信息顺序和合理但不正确的输出的敏感度的限制"
  },
  "Latent Diffusion Models (LDMs) have become dominant in visual synthesis, but their quality-compute trade-off is largely constrained by the tokenizer's fixed compression ratio": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:39.406345+00:00",
    "zh": "潜在扩散模型（ LDM ）在视觉合成中占据主导地位，但它们的质量-计算权衡在很大程度上受到标记器固定压缩比的限制"
  },
  "Leveraging Vision Foundation Models (VFMs) for camera-to-LiDAR knowledge distillation offers a promising solution to the scarcity of annotated data needed to represent the immense geometric and kinematic diversity of real-world autonomous driving (AD)": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:38.542595+00:00",
    "zh": "利用视觉基础模型（ VFM ）进行相机到LiDAR的知识提取，为代表现实世界自动驾驶（ AD ）的巨大几何和运动多样性所需的注释数据的稀缺性提供了一个有前途的解决方案"
  },
  "Low-rank adaptation (LoRA) makes it cheap to train many domain- and task-specific language model adapters, but whether two adapters can be merged is usually discovered only after both have been fully trained and evaluated": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:23.464909+00:00",
    "zh": "低秩自适应（ LoRA ）使得训练许多特定领域和任务的语言模型适配器变得便宜，但通常只有在两个适配器都经过充分训练和评估后才能发现是否可以合并两个适配器"
  },
  "Mainstream LLM serving systems reuse prefix work mainly through paged or radix key-value (KV) caches": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:34.109260+00:00",
    "zh": "主流LLM服务系统重用前缀主要通过分页或基数键值(KV)缓存工作"
  },
  "Modern LLM training breaks a core assumption behind offline batch samplers: the true training cost of a sample is only observable after preprocessing, augmentation, templating, tokenization, and multimodal visual-token expansion": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:29.896986+00:00",
    "zh": "现代LLM培训打破了离线批量采样器背后的核心假设：样本的真实培训成本只有在预处理、增强、模板化、标记化和多模态可视化令牌扩展后才能观察到"
  },
  "Multi-agent reinforcement learning (MARL) enables agents to develop coordination strategies through emergent communication, but neural policies lack the formal safety guarantees required for safety-critical robotic deployment in drone swarms and autonomous veh": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T06:56:22.539936+00:00",
    "zh": "多智能体强化学习（ MARL ）使智能体能够通过紧急沟通制定协调策略，但神经政策缺乏在无人机群和自主VEH中部署安全关键机器人所需的正式安全保障"
  },
  "MultiModal Federated Graph Learning (MM-FGL) offers a natural collaborative training paradigm, but its practical deployment is challenged by two granularities of modality imbalance": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:03.089768+00:00",
    "zh": "多模态联合图学习（ MM-FGL ）提供了一种自然的协作训练范式，但其实际部署受到两种模态不平衡粒度的挑战"
  },
  "Multimodal Large Language Models (MLLMs) often lose track of the right image regions during fine-grained spatial reasoning, because a textual query rarely carries any explicit geometric anchor into the pixel domain": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:15.106474+00:00",
    "zh": "多模态大语言模型（ MLLM ）在精细的空间推理过程中经常会丢失正确的图像区域，因为文本查询很少将任何显式的几何锚点带入像素域"
  },
  "Multimodal foundation models have advanced rapidly thanks to large optical benchmarks, but comparable resources for synthetic aperture radar (SAR) remain limited": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:01.602523+00:00",
    "zh": "得益于大型光学基准，多模态基础模型已迅速发展，但合成孔径雷达（ SAR ）的可比资源仍然有限"
  },
  "Multimodal large language models (MLLMs) are increasingly deployed in personally and societally consequential settings, yet the visual cues that shape how these models judge people remain poorly understood": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:00.807129+00:00",
    "zh": "多模态大语言模型（ MLM ）越来越多地部署在个人和社会重要环境中，但这些模型如何判断人们的视觉线索仍然知之甚少"
  },
  "Physics-informed neural networks (PINNs) have become a powerful framework for solving PDEs by embedding physical laws into differentiable objectives": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:11.399757+00:00",
    "zh": "物理知情神经网络（ PINN ）已成为通过将物理定律嵌入到可微目标中来解决PDE的强大框架"
  },
  "Real-world clinical decision support requires reasoning over heterogeneous and longitudinal patient information rather than answering isolated medical questions": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:10.631716+00:00",
    "zh": "真实世界的临床决策支持需要对异质和纵向的患者信息进行推理，而不是回答孤立的医疗问题"
  },
  "Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) improves factual grounding, but it also lengthens prompts and raises prefill cost": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-19T22:13:45.277548+00:00",
    "zh": "检索增强生成（ RAG ）改善了事实基础，但也延长了提示并提高了预填充成本"
  },
  "Safety is a core concern for deploying reinforcement learning (RL) agents in real-world domains such as robotics and autonomous driving": {
    "source": "mymemory",
    "updated_at": "2026-06-20T22:21:05.966985+00:00",
    "zh": "在机器人和自动驾驶等现实领域部署强化学习（ RL ）代理时，安全是核心问题"
  },
  "Streaming video generation is emerging as a new serving workload in which users interact with long-lived sessions that generate video progressively, chunk by chunk": {
